data.description: Beautiful lake views from this 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom 2 Story end unit home. Great room overlooks the lake. Split bedroom floor plan upstairs with a convenient full size washer/dryer closet with storage. Master bedroom overlooks the expansive lake & has an en-suite bathroom with a large walk-in closet. Riverwalk is a guard gated, ''all age'' community that's centrally located & convenient to everything.Beautiful well maintained community. Close to Turnpike and I-95. Downtown, City place with fine restaurants and shops. Close to airport. Located in the highly sought after RIVERWALK community, Resort style living, play a set of tennis, meet friends for a light lunch at cafe, enjoy 12 miles of scenic pathways, take a quick swim or enjoy a vigorous workout in the fitness center.
